  displayName: "Feelings\u2026?"
  dialogueOne: How have you been feeling lately?
  dialogueTwo: ... To be honest with you, psychiatrist told me I'm showing some symptoms
    of [depression] lately. I suppose that might be how I'm feeling.
  dialogueThree: I'm really sorry to hear that. I appreciate you feeling comfortable
    enough to share this with me.
  nextSO: 
  symptomSO: Dealing with Depression
  devNotes: 
